00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:18.100 align:middle line:84%
Remote viewing is
a skill people can

00:21:18.100 --> 00:21:21.680 align:middle line:84%
learn to discern information
not only across space,

00:21:21.680 --> 00:21:23.110 align:middle line:90%
but across time.

00:21:23.110 --> 00:21:26.440 align:middle line:84%
And the fact that the scientific
community that is open

00:21:26.440 --> 00:21:28.720 align:middle line:84%
minded scientists
