00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:31.240 align:middle line:84%
these cases in human
beings who have them

00:21:31.240 --> 00:21:33.370 align:middle line:84%
and then try and
explain it all, it's

00:21:33.370 --> 00:21:37.270 align:middle line:84%
very comforting that they are
supporting the reality of this.

00:21:37.270 --> 00:21:39.880 align:middle line:84%
So what we're
beginning to realize

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:44.230 align:middle line:84%
is the arrow of causality
is not brain events cause

00:21:44.230 --> 00:21:47.200 align:middle line:84%
mental and phenomenal events,
but it works the other way

00:21:47.200 --> 00:21:50.620 align:middle line:84%
around, that, in
fact, mind over matter

00:21:50.620 --> 00:21:52.900 align:middle line:84%
is the general
principle at work here.

00:21:52.900 --> 00:21:56.440 align:middle line:84%
And that's an extraordinary
gift of understanding

00:21:56.440 --> 00:21:59.050 align:middle line:84%
because it helps us
understand the afterlife, all

00:21:59.050 --> 00:22:01.600 align:middle line:84%
the scientific evidence
for reincarnation.

00:22:01.600 --> 00:22:03.970 align:middle line:84%
Every bit of it starts
to make more sense when

00:22:03.970 --> 00:22:06.910 align:middle line:84%
we see the brain not as a
producer of consciousness,

00:22:06.910 --> 00:22:10.810 align:middle line:84%
