to project a little eddy

00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:17.420 align:middle line:84%
current of consciousness that
we interpret as our own mind,

00:22:17.420 --> 00:22:19.660 align:middle line:84%
and yet ultimately,
they're all linked together

00:22:19.660 --> 00:22:22.360 align:middle line:84%
as we traverse through
that veil and reunite

00:22:22.360 --> 00:22:25.030 align:middle line:90%
with that primordial mind.

00:22:25.030 --> 00:22:27.830 align:middle line:84%
>> And so for me, the
