everywhere in the world,

00:22:41.560 --> 00:22:44.180 align:middle line:84%
this electromagnetic
information field.

00:22:44.180 --> 00:22:47.110 align:middle line:84%
But you need an
instrument to receive it

00:22:47.110 --> 00:22:50.620 align:middle line:84%
and you put on your computer,
