code you have, you

00:22:59.380 --> 00:23:01.630 align:middle line:84%
receive your personal
consciousness.

00:23:01.630 --> 00:23:05.710 align:middle line:84%
So death, for me, is the
end of a physical body,

00:23:05.710 --> 00:23:08.140 align:middle line:84%
