00:23:36.890 --> 00:23:39.220 align:middle line:90%
They're frightened.

00:23:39.220 --> 00:23:41.380 align:middle line:84%
>> That's the problem
with materialist science,

00:23:41.380 --> 00:23:45.880 align:middle line:84%
is their main approach to this
has been to debunk and deny,

00:23:45.880 --> 00:23:47.440 align:middle line:90%
to dismiss.

00:23:47.440 --> 00:23:49.930 align:middle line:84%
There are scientists on
record saying my case was

00:23:49.930 --> 00:23:52.190 align:middle line:90%
nonsense, how could it happen?

00:23:52.190 --> 00:23:55.640 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's the big
mystery, how could it happen?

00:23:55.640 --> 00:23:57.350 align:middle line:10%
And that's what we're
trying to explain.

00:23:57.350 --> 00:24:02.710 align:middle line:84%
But when scientists obscure
data, when they intentionally

00:24:02.710 --> 00:24:05.840 align:middle line:84%
cover up, debunk,
deny, sweep evidence

00:24:05.840 --> 00:24:09.230 align:middle line:84%
under the rug, all they're
doing is cheating themselves.

00:24:09.230 --> 00:24:11.930 align:middle line:84%
We need to take all
of human experience

00:24:11.930 --> 00:24:14.630 align:middle line:84%
and try and come up with
a better explanation.

00:24:14.630 --> 00:24:17.030 align:middle line:10%
That's where I think
the scientific study

00:24:17.030 --> 00:24:19.640 align:middle line:10%
of consciousness, and
this includes the science

00:24:19.640 --> 00:24:22.940 align:middle line:10%
