the science of reincarnation,

00:24:22.940 --> 00:24:26.050 align:middle line:10%
because that data is
extremely powerful and really

00:24:26.050 --> 00:24:26.850 align:middle line:10%
overwhelming.

00:24:26.850 --> 00:24:27.720 align:middle line:10%
You can't deny it.

00:24:27.720 --> 00:24:29.240 align:middle line:10%
Once you start to
read that data,

00:24:29.240 --> 00:24:31.400 align:middle line:10%
and understand how
it was assembled,

00:24:31.400 --> 00:24:33.260 align:middle line:10%
and the respect
for the scientists

00:24:33.260 --> 00:24:35.540 align:middle line:10%
like Ian Stevenson
