00:24:38.220 --> 00:24:40.790 align:middle line:10%
and we realized that
it's really up to science

00:24:40.790 --> 00:24:43.400 align:middle line:10%
to accept all the
empirical data and then try

00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:44.310 align:middle line:10%
to make sense of it.

00:24:44.310 --> 00:24:46.580 align:middle line:84%
And that's what's
finally happening.

00:24:46.580 --> 00:24:50.030 align:middle line:84%
>> I am a skeptic, by the
