00:26:41.650 --> 00:26:43.840 align:middle line:90%
change the way you live.

00:26:43.840 --> 00:26:46.420 align:middle line:90%
So it's not that easy at all.

00:26:46.420 --> 00:26:50.590 align:middle line:84%
That's the challenge,
