00:27:09.220 --> 00:27:12.120 align:middle line:84%
And I had 18 episodes of
respiratory failure in 2 and 1/2

00:27:12.120 --> 00:27:12.920 align:middle line:90%
years.

00:27:12.920 --> 00:27:14.950 align:middle line:10%
And I had made friends
