00:27:20.030 --> 00:27:23.410 align:middle line:10%
And he had invited me several
times to come on his show

00:27:23.410 --> 00:27:24.530 align:middle line:10%
and share my story.

00:27:24.530 --> 00:27:25.988 align:middle line:84%
And I would come
up with any reason

00:27:25.988 --> 00:27:27.770 align:middle line:90%
I could think of not to do it.

00:27:27.770 --> 00:27:30.460 align:middle line:84%
So the last time that I went
