me, what are you doing?

00:27:40.610 --> 00:27:42.970 align:middle line:84%
And he said, it's
not me, it's you.

00:27:42.970 --> 00:27:45.230 align:middle line:84%
And I was like, what
do you mean it's me?

00:27:45.230 --> 00:27:47.360 align:middle line:10%
These doctors can't figure
out what's going on.

00:27:47.360 --> 00:27:48.470 align:middle line:10%
I can't fix this.

00:27:48.470 --> 00:27:50.370 align:middle line:90%
And he said, you can fix this?

00:27:50.370 --> 00:27:52.170 align:middle line:84%
You said you were
going to go back.

00:27:52.170 --> 00:27:54.080 align:middle line:90%
You said you were going to live.

00:27:54.080 --> 00:27:56.780 align:middle line:84%
And every time I put an
opportunity in front of you

00:27:56.780 --> 00:28:00.230 align:middle line:84%
or somebody for you
to love, you say no.

00:28:00.230 --> 00:28:02.810 align:middle line:90%
Do you want to go back and live?

00:28:02.810 --> 00:28:04.050 align:middle line:90%
And I said, yes.

00:28:04.050 --> 00:28:05.973 align:middle line:84%
He said, well, then
start saying yes.

00:28:05.973 --> 00:28:08.390 align:middle line:84%
And I just thought it was the
most ridiculous thing I ever

00:28:08.390 --> 00:28:09.190 align:middle line:90%
heard.

00:28:09.190 --> 00:28:11.300 align:middle line:84%
I said, so you're
telling me if I go back

00:28:11.300 --> 00:28:14.190 align:middle line:84%
