I'm going to be healed?

00:28:14.190 --> 00:28:15.293 align:middle line:90%
And he said, yes.

00:28:15.293 --> 00:28:17.960 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, well, that sounds
like the most insane thing I've

00:28:17.960 --> 00:28:20.520 align:middle line:84%
