stop myself, I said yes.

00:28:32.930 --> 00:28:35.150 align:middle line:84%
And I went and did that
talk, and I have never

00:28:35.150 --> 00:28:37.780 align:middle line:90%
had another episode since.

00:28:37.780 --> 00:28:41.680 align:middle line:84%
>> And that is why people who
