be chasing something.

00:28:49.610 --> 00:28:53.210 align:middle line:84%
I've spent my whole
life chasing knowledge.

00:28:53.210 --> 00:28:55.840 align:middle line:84%
Some people spend
their life chasing

00:28:55.840 --> 00:28:58.600 align:middle line:84%
money, or fame, or
power, or whatever

00:28:58.600 --> 00:29:00.350 align:middle line:90%
